# Raw Meeting Data Directory

Place your meeting transcripts and summaries here.

Supported formats:
- .txt files
- .json files  
- .md files
- .docx files

## Example JSON structure:

```json
{
  "title": "Enterprise Client Discovery Call",
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "client": "TechCorp Inc",
  "participants": ["John Smith (Sales)", "Jane Doe (Client)", "Mike Johnson (Technical)"],
  "summary": "Initial discovery call with enterprise client...",
  "key_points": [
    "Budget range: $50k-100k",
    "Timeline: Q2 implementation",
    "Main concern: data security"
  ],
  "objections": "Concerned about integration complexity",
  "pricing_discussion": "Discussed enterprise tier pricing",
  "next_steps": ["Send security documentation", "Schedule technical demo"]
}
```

## Example Text format:

```
# Meeting: TechCorp Discovery Call

## Date
2024-01-15

## Client  
TechCorp Inc

## Participants
John Smith (Sales), Jane Doe (Client)

## Summary
Initial discovery call with enterprise client...

## Key Points
- Budget range: $50k-100k
- Timeline: Q2 implementation  
- Main concern: data security

## Objections
Concerned about integration complexity

## Next Steps
- Send security documentation
- Schedule technical demo
```